data.text:
We believe in creating a space where people can encounter God, learn the Word, and discover God's plan for your life! Come, join us and you'll feel right at home.

Pastors Jeremy & Lisa founded Faith World Harvest Church in 2001. The emphasis of their ministry is empowering believers to live victoriously and to take Jesus to the world. They are committed to equipping those who come to FW by teaching the powerful truths of God's love, faith, grace, healing, and righteousness. Through preaching of the Word and a move of the Holy Spirit, they are raising up a congregation passionate about God, and reaching the lost! Jeremy has a Doctorates Degree in theology and ministerial ethics from School of Bible Theology Seminary and University. Lisa is a graduate of Rhema Bible Training Center and has earned a Masters Degree from SBTSU. They live in Hemet California with their three sons: Nick, Parker, and Roman.
